  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very interesting that, by that time, instructions started to appear for, for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] moving out and relocating ourselves in a-- in a-- the term-- in a pre-determined, confined area, which became the ghetto later on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That worried me no end because, I mean, my poor mother looked after our, our very little flat so impeccably.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You know, and the thought of, of-- well, we lived there, by that time, 20 years, right, should be-- should be left.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, we had this very typical, typical bourgeois attitude.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have a great deal of other assets, but that piece of furniture that, you know, was, was was all-important.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they called me up-- and by that time, I knew exactly that the, the ghettoization will happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That filled me with tremendous concern.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I knew that they will not be able to do it physically, you know, physically-- I mean, the sheer logistics of it, right, to move those things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and not knowing where they are going to go, whom they are going to live with filled me with, with considerable worry and concern.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, there's nothing I could do about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was-- I left on the 15th of May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew that, you know, that was the last.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] And, [CRYING] and I was called up to Jolsva, actually.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Jolsva is a-- is a place-- [CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] is a-- is a place in Hungary, in northern Hungary, where the Jewish boys concentration occurred.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember we, we, we traveled together with my friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were all called up at this, this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] age group.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
